headline: Got $1,000? 1 Underrated Artificial Intelligence Stock to Buy During the Nasdaq's Latest Correction
summary: Less than three months ago, the Nasdaq Composite hit an all-time high, continuing a solid run that began two years ago.  As an index heavily influenced by large tech stocks, it's no surprise that many big-name tech stocks have followed the same fate this year.  While many tech companies dealing with artificial intelligence (AI) experienced surges over the past couple of years, that same hype (or lack thereof) has led to some significant drops alongside the Nasdaq correction.
